## المرحلة 1: إنشاء `LookupSchoolType`

#### [NEW] إضافة model في Prisma

```prisma
model LookupSchoolType {
  id          Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  code        String    @unique @db.VarChar(50)
  nameAr      String    @map("name_ar") @db.VarChar(100)
  isActive    Boolean   @default(true) @map("is_active")
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now()) @map("created_at")
  updatedAt   DateTime  @updatedAt @map("updated_at")
  deletedAt   DateTime? @map("deleted_at")
  createdById String?   @map("created_by") @db.VarChar(191)
  updatedById String?   @map("updated_by") @db.VarChar(191)

  createdBy      User?           @relation("lookup_school_type_created_by", ...)
  updatedBy      User?           @relation("lookup_school_type_updated_by", ...)
  schoolProfiles SchoolProfile[]

  @@map("lookup_school_types")
}
```

#### [NEW] بيانات Seed أولية

| Code | الاسم العربي |
|------|-------------|
| `BOYS` | بنين |
| `GIRLS` | بنات |
| `MIXED` | مختلط |

